<br>
'Queen Pallas, let me introduce myself to you. I am Poseidon, brother of Zeus and his equal in dignity. I've come to you to partake of friendship. I know many amazons do not care much for male dieties but I do not care for your worship. We are both royalty and I hope you can make descisions that are not too rash. Here I have a gift for you.'<br>
<br>
::He gently rubs the mares large white mane.::<br>
<br>
'It is a mare bred in my stables and it is immortal. She can talk and she will eat what horses normally eat. Please except this as an token of my friendship. I will be pleased if we can have a lasting relationship that will sprout and grow.' <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 10/27/01 3:38:15 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.showMessage?topicID=26.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.showMessage?topicID=12.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.emailToFriend?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.threadControl?topicID=24.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm30.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=24.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll 